{"tid":1976283,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"下世代遊戲既新基準RTX,Minecraft 都變神畫面","createTime":"2020-04-17T06:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T09:00:50.000Z","uid":56731,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"99acd864d84bc54f70b2a9b2d4c3f47e85eb6566","tid":1976283,"uid":56731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T06:37:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yq6lecRKyjU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fyq6lecRKyjU&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU94c%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=7f09a0ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yq6lecRKyjU</a><br />\n作為遊戲開發準則既PS同Xbox下世代開始支援光線追蹤技術<br />\n畫面又向真實進一大步，連minecraft都可以唔駛mod就靚到暈<br />\nMinecraft Rex 岩岩出咗bate<br />\n同真實一樣既光影，唔同材質有唔同既反射<br />\n依家你見到好多支援光線追蹤既遊戲仲係後加上去，真係好期待用光線追蹤做基礎開發既遊戲可以幾靚<br />\n所有反射唔駛另外整個model出嚟，多唔少資源係其他地方打磨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ATFKUQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ATFKUQ.jpg&h=24812470&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kTwoHGw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkTwoHGw.jpg&h=5d9de66d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"daf58a69a7ed7575410d1c1086767d1f8484a557","tid":1976283,"uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T07:33:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e1b087f612eacd3853706f8d3ddcaa0740b384","tid":1976283,"uid":56731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:00:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UHAdmfT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUHAdmfT.png&h=fdc2cf07&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cUdFLHz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcUdFLHz.png&h=05cfdde4&s={SIZE}